QuestData.Title: Proof of Strength: Orc Thorn
QuestData.Description: This thorn is proof of your strength at slaying the infested and your gladiator friend has born witness!$b$bTake the thorn back to Limbflayer and claim your accolades!
QuestData.LogDescription: Take the proof to Limbflayer at Beastwatch in Gorgrond.
